{"tid":959333,"cid":21,"subCid":0,"title":"其實陳詠謙有咩問題","createTime":"2018-12-28T13:25:27.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-28T13:44:56.000Z","uid":219341,"like":8,"dislike":27,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"23b35b3e87effc9b6e496517b1fdfeda5ef213dc","tid":959333,"uid":219341,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T13:25:27.000Z","msg":"佢作詞既好多歌其實都好聽<br />\n漸漸<br />\n認真如初<br />\n在月台上等你<br />\n難得一遇<br />\nDear Jane三部曲<br />\n一雙手<br />\n別來無恙<br />\n回眸一笑<br />\n等等等等....<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n屌班柒頭係又屌唔係又屌<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n基本上每個創作人既作品都唔會全部都出名<br />\n全部都合乎大家既心意㗎啦<br />\n係咪佢地啲全部作品都要超曬班咁先叫合格<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n創作本來就好難做到全部維持高水準<br />\n自己笑自己人 仲要係咁做比較 屌你老母係咪on9㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  好似梵高同畢加索唔同畫家唔同畫風咁<br />\n每個人風格不一 根本無得分高下 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bomb.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 創作呢樣嘢本來就好主觀 再係咁落去香港地仲會有邊個有勇氣膽量去做創作<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n香港人咁撚樣 唔怪得變文化沙漠啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n尊重創作唔撚該 試吓唔好屌<br />\n而係比多啲有用既意見<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/flowerface.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"27ece5793f05f6cfdd17864b42b4a8ac7711622b","tid":959333,"uid":38904,"like":0,"dislike":2,"score":-2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T13:26:47.000Z","msg":"連開 po 抒發己見都唔得？"},{"pid":"cd93e1feca368f64840514c9d52eac083d793a4c","tid":959333,"uid":176802,"like":23,"dislike":0,"score":23,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T13:28:31.000Z","msg":"好聽係因為<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">作曲作得好呀屌你老母</span><br />\n首詞的而且確係垃撚圾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"718be61c83ae15c86c8db4d277c6771f4e0d1fb8","tid":959333,"uid":207646,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-28T13:29:02.000Z","msg":"陳生開左個連登ac?<img src